title: Kokuhaku
overview: A psychological thriller of a grieving mother turned cold-blooded avenger with a twisty master plan to pay back those who were responsible for her daughter's death.

title: Network
overview: A television network cynically exploits a deranged former anchor's ravings and revelations about the news media for its own profit.

title: Jungfrukällan
overview: An innocent yet pampered young virgin and her family's pregnant and jealous servant set out to deliver candles to church, but only one returns from events that transpire in the woods along the way.

title: Vozvrashchenie
overview: In the Russian wilderness, two brothers face a range of new, conflicting emotions when their father - a man they know only through a single photograph - resurfaces.

title: Sling Blade
overview: Karl Childers, a simple man hospitalized since his childhood murder of his mother and her lover, is released to start a new life in a small town.

title: Udaan
overview: Expelled from his school, a 16-year old boy returns home to his abusive and oppressive father.

title: Magnolia
overview: An epic mosaic of interrelated characters in search of love, forgiveness, and meaning in the San Fernando Valley.

title: Boyhood
overview: The life of Mason, from early childhood to his arrival at college.

title: Mommy
overview: A widowed single mother, raising her violent son alone, finds new hope when a mysterious neighbor inserts herself into their household.

title: Roma
overview: A year in the life of a middle-class family's maid in Mexico City in the early 1970s.
stars: ['Yalitza Aparicio', 'Marina de Tavira', 'Diego Cortina Autrey', 'Carlos Peralta']

title: Kagemusha
overview: A petty thief with an utter resemblance to a samurai warlord is hired as the lord's double. When the warlord later dies the thief is forced to take up arms in his place.

title: Anand
overview: The story of a terminally ill man who wishes to live life to the fullest before the inevitable occurs, as told by his best friend.

title: Gattaca
overview: A genetically inferior man assumes the identity of a superior one in order to pursue his lifelong dream of space travel.

title: Okuribito
overview: A newly unemployed cellist takes a job preparing the dead for funerals.

title: Capharnaüm
overview: While serving a five-year sentence for a violent crime, a 12-year-old boy sues his parents for neglect.
stars: ['Zain Al Rafeea', 'Yordanos Shiferaw', 'Boluwatife Treasure Bankole', 'Kawsar Al Haddad']

title: Nelyubov
overview: A couple going through a divorce must team up to find their son who has disappeared during one of their bitter arguments.

title: Freaks
overview: A circus' beautiful trapeze artist agrees to marry the leader of side-show performers, but his deformed friends discover she is only marrying him for his inheritance.

title: Jagten
overview: A teacher lives a lonely life, all the while struggling over his son's custody. His life slowly gets better as he finds love and receives good news from his son, but his new luck is about to be brutally shattered by an innocent little lie.

title: Höstsonaten
overview: A married daughter who longs for her mother's love is visited by the latter, a successful concert pianist.

title: Room
overview: Held captive for 7 years in an enclosed space, a woman and her young son finally gain their freedom, allowing the boy to experience the outside world for the first time.
